OL,3,CProgramme listings for SUN 8 MAR
OL,4,G1605FKirstie and Phil's Love It or
OL,5,     FList It
OL,6,     GKirstie Allsopp and Phil Spencer
OL,7,     Gmeet the Farhall family in
OL,8,     GWindsor. Nardeth is fed up with
OL,9,     Gthe layout of their four-bed
OL,10,     Gdetached home, but Graham loves
OL,11,     Gthe location.
OL,12,G1715FLocation, Location, Location
OL,13,     GKirstie house-hunts with a pair
OL,14,     Gof nervous first-time buyers in
OL,15,     GBalham and Putney in south west
OL,16,     GLondon. Phil looks for a big,
OL,17,     GAussie-style property in the
OL,18,     GThames Valley.
