OL,4,G1955FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GFor the final visit the B&Bers go
OL,6,     Gglamping again, at Phil and
OL,7,     GJane's site in Derbyshire, where
OL,8,     Gthe stag-gering views include
OL,9,     Greal-life deer wandering about
OL,10,     Gthe place.
OL,11,G2025FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GOn payment day, the B&Bers clash
OL,13,     Gover furniture failings and clock
OL,14,     Gcomplaints. And sparks fly -
OL,15,     Gironically - over a lack of
OL,16,     Gelectricity. Who's won?
