OL,4,G2100F999: On the Front Line
OL,5,     GBrand new series: Paramedics
OL,6,     Gtreat a man having a heart attack
OL,7,     Gwho thinks he's just pulled a
OL,8,     Gmuscle. And a day out hiking ends
OL,9,     Gbadly for a man who's fallen and
OL,10,     Ginjured his ankle.
OL,11,G2200F24 Hours in A&E
OL,12,     GThis episode meets people who've
OL,13,     Gtaken big risks and explores how
OL,14,     Git's affected their lives.
OL,15,     GMotorbikers James and Peter are
OL,16,     Gboth rushed in. Ex-miner Alfred
OL,17,     Ghas severe chest pain.
