OL,11,G0005F999: On the Front Line
OL,12,     GParamedics treat a woman with a
OL,13,     Gpossible bleed on the brain, a
OL,14,     Gbaby whose heart is beating
OL,15,     Gextremely fast, a man showing
OL,16,     Gsigns of a stroke, and a woman
OL,17,     Gwho may have sepsis.
